<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07833</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INSTITUTIONALIZING PRE-SCHOOL EDUCATION, INCREASING THE MONTHLY COMPENSATION OF DAY CARE WORKERS AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Institutionalizes pre-school education as part of the compulsory basic education and provides that Barangay Day Care Centers (R.A. 6972) constitute said public sector institution; Mandates pre-school teachers to continuously undergo the necessary trainings and provides for their monthly basic salary based on the compensation of public school teachers under the SSL, as amended; Enumerates the functions of the DSWD and qualifications and appointment of day care workers.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ALEJANO, GARY C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-05-31</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Del Mar (000 2018-08-01)</td><td>2. Tambunting (000 2018-10-07)</td><tr><td>3. Sangcopan (000 2018-10-10)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON BASIC EDUCATION AND CULTURE ON 2018-07-30</td></tr></table>